{"tid":672991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有payme, applepay, 八達通就夠。唔撚使we7支付寶","createTime":"2018-05-21T12:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T08:44:04.000Z","uid":47359,"like":111,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"03df74d19380b0538cebe75db0b51e6d98bc068b","tid":672991,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛無敵logic: xxx推qr code=&gt;qr code好</span><br />\n實情係香港赤化中, 劣幣驅逐良幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.payme用嚟人與人過細數。<br />\npayme匯豐出, we7支付寶中國出, security你信邊個?<br />\n<br />\n2.applepay googlepay直情係credit 卡。我一路喺連登屌柒D wade 姐打羅夫JR dewi呢啲五毛一隊個電話埋去拍1秒就得。<br />\n支付寶又要開app又要掃code唔知幾多秒又要綁信用卡/入錢，又慢又麻煩<br />\n<br />\n3.班五毛成撚日話細商鋪免支付寶裝機費<br />\n問題係細鋪連8仔都唔撚會裝, 唔想報稅。二嚟用cash交易唔會特別慢<br />\n<br />\n4.八仔有自動增值<br />\n<br />\n5.大額交易咪又係用返卡<br />\n<br />\n6.商鋪俾人貼個假code就呃到錢。好兒戲<br />\n<br />\n7.nfc交易安全過qr code</blockquote>"},{"pid":"86e9eec38445df7b7ffa7423b6aafb1fc47961d7","tid":672991,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320efcb2c729a260e2e3eb9f52fb29ea16e2ed87","tid":672991,"uid":55,"like":10,"dislike":7,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e734aa4b7893d61f0c30e513f71bfc64a137e2f6","tid":672991,"uid":47359,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"320efcb2c729a260e2e3eb9f52fb29ea16e2ed87","tid":672991,"uid":55,"like":10,"dislike":7,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:25:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛返六日唔撚易<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/212504_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2